{{2018 Asian Games}}
'''第十八屆亞洲運動會'''（{{lang-en|'''Jakarta Palembang 2018 Asian Games'''}}）是於2018年8月18日至9月2日在[[印尼|印尼]]首都[[雅加達|雅加達]]舉行的[[亚洲运动会|亞洲運動會]]。<ref>{{cite news|title=Jakarta to host the 2018 Asian Games|date=2014-09-19|newspaper=The Jakarta Post|url=http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2014/09/19/jakarta-host-2018-asian-games.html|accessdate=2014-09-19|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101004232/https://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2014/09/19/jakarta-host-2018-asian-games.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[巨港|巨港]]和[[萬隆|萬隆]]是協辦城市。<ref name="antara"/>2014年9月19日，[[亞奧理事會|亞奧理事會]]執行委員會宣布由印尼獲得本屆賽事的主辦權。<ref>{{cite news|title=Asian Games: Indonesia to host Asiad in 2018, says OCA chief|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/sport/asian-games-indonesia-to/1370174.html|accessdate=2014-04-19|newspaper=Channel News Asia|date=2014-09-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140922001350/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/sport/asian-games-indonesia-to/1370174.html|archivedate=2014-09-22}}</ref>為了避開[[印尼總統|印尼總統]]選舉，賽事提前於2018年舉辦，而不是原計劃中的2019年。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Davies|first1=Will|title=Indonesia to Host 2018 Asian Games|url=http://online.wsj.com/articles/indonesia-to-host-2018-asian-games-1411189198|accessdate=2014-09-27|publisher=The Wall Street Journal|date=2014-09-20|archive-date=2014-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140926031117/http://online.wsj.com/articles/indonesia-to-host-2018-asian-games-1411189198|dead-url=no}}</ref>

本屆賽事原本的主辦城市為[[越南|越南]][[河內|河內]]，<ref name=cost />因為財政問題而放棄主辦。<ref name=withdrew />

== 申辦過程 ==
{| class="wikitable" style="float:right; clear:both; margin-left:.5em; margin-top:.1em;"
|colspan=3 align=center|'''[[亞洲奧林匹克理事會|亞洲奧林匹克理事會]]第31次會議'''<br /><small>2012年11月8日，於[[澳門|澳門]]舉行。</small>
|- bgcolor="#efefef"
| '''候選城市'''
| '''國家奥委会'''
| bgcolor="silver"|'''第一輪'''
|-
|[[河內|河內]]||{{VIE}}||'''29'''
|-
|[[泗水_(印尼)|泗水]]||{{INA}}||14
|}

2012年11月8日，在第31届亚奥理事会会员大会上，越南[[河内|河内]]将和印尼[[泗水市|泗水市]]和阿联酋[[迪拜|迪拜]]争夺赛事主办权。河内最终以29比14的票数击败泗水市胜出<ref name=Indonesia>{{cite news|last=Adamrah|first=Mustaqim|title=RI loses Asian Games bid to Vietnam|url=http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2012/11/09/ri-loses-asian-games-bid-vietnam.html|accessdate=2012-11-09|newspaper=The Jakarta Post|date=2012-11-09|archive-date=2012-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121111065637/http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2012/11/09/ri-loses-asian-games-bid-vietnam.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。迪拜在最后关头弃权，宣布把重心放在之后的申办中。阿联酋国家奥委会副主席否认弃权，表示迪拜“不申请举办2019年亚运会”，“只是考虑过”这样做<ref name=cost>{{cite news|title=Hanoi wins race to host 2019 Asian Games|url=http://www.thestar.com.my/story/?file=%2f2012%2f11%2f8%2fsports%2f20121108190745&sec=sports|accessdate=2012-11-08|newspaper=The Star|date=2012-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151107080546/http://www.thestar.com.my/story/?file=%2f2012%2f11%2f8%2fsports%2f20121108190745&sec=sports|archive-date=2015-11-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Sambidge|first=Andy|title=UAE denies Asian Games 2019 vote pull-out|url=http://www.arabianbusiness.com/uae-denies-asian-games-2019-vote-pull-out-478996.html|accessdate=2012-11-14|newspaper=Arabian Business|date=2012-11-09|archive-date=2012-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121112211641/http://www.arabianbusiness.com/uae-denies-asian-games-2019-vote-pull-out-478996.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Tam|first=Aaron|title=Hanoi wins race to host 2019 Asian Games: officials|url=https://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5jGC0GGZ8VOz-TBKeA0kPpDELUooA?docId=CNG.ac5dd23b4cb60fe50b9a88f18598f36b.2b1|accessdate=2012-11-09|newspaper=AFP|date=2012-11-09}}</ref>。

2014年3月，越南传出问题，1.5亿美元的预算可能超支，最终花费有望超过3亿。此外，评论员认为[[2003年東南亞運動會|2003年東南亞運動會]]时建造的场馆一直没有用过<ref>{{cite news|title=Vietnam lawmakers concerned by mounting cost of Asian Games|url=http://www.thanhniennews.com/sports/vietnam-lawmakers-concerned-by-mounting-cost-of-asian-games-24816.html|accessdate=2014-03-26|newspaper=Thanh Nien News|date=2014-03-26|archive-date=2014-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140326164255/http://www.thanhniennews.com/sports/vietnam-lawmakers-concerned-by-mounting-cost-of-asian-games-24816.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。越南奥委会前主席何光譽也表示举办亚运会不会促进旅游业发展<ref>{{cite news|title=Vietnam PM could pull plug on Asian Games|url=http://www.thanhniennews.com/sports/vietnam-pm-could-pull-plug-on-asian-games-25086.html|accessdate=2014-04-15|newspaper=Thanh Nien News|date=2014-04-07|archive-date=2014-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140416184110/http://www.thanhniennews.com/sports/vietnam-pm-could-pull-plug-on-asian-games-25086.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年4月7日，越南总理[[阮晋勇|阮晋勇]]正式宣布河内放弃举办<ref name=withdrew>{{cite news|title=Vietnam backs out as hosts of 2019 Asian Games|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2014/04/17/us-games-asia-vietnam-idUSBREA3G18H20140417|accessdate=2014-04-17|newspaper=Reuters|date=2014-04-17|archive-date=2014-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140417235926/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/04/17/us-games-asia-vietnam-idUSBREA3G18H20140417|dead-url=no}}</ref>，得到越南民众支持<ref>{{cite news|title=Vietnamese hail PM's decision to relinquish 2019 Asiad|url=http://tuoitrenews.vn/sports/19089/vietnamese-hails-pms-decision-to-relinquish-asiad|first=Tuoi|last=Tre|accessdate=2014-04-19|newspaper=Tuoi Tre|date=2014-04-17|archive-date=2014-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140420004947/http://tuoitrenews.vn/sports/19089/vietnamese-hails-pms-decision-to-relinquish-asiad|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Asian Games: No penalty for Vietnam pullout, says OCA|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/sport/asian-games-no-penalty/1081772.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140424161458/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/sport/asian-games-no-penalty/1081772.html|archivedate=2014-04-24|accessdate=2014-04-24|newspaper=Channel News Asia|date=2014-04-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他表示弃权的主要原因是毫无准备和经济衰退，国家无法负担设施和场地的建设费用<ref name=withdrew />。

越南弃权后，亚奥理事会表示印尼、中国和阿联酋是主办权的主要竞争者<ref>{{cite news|last=Thongsombat|first=Kittipong|title=Trio vying to host 2019 Asian Games|url=http://www.bangkokpost.com/news/sports/407346/trio-vying-to-host-2019-asian-games|accessdate=2014-04-30|newspaper=Bangkok Post|date=2014-04-30}}</ref>。普遍认为，上次申办排第二的印尼很有可能胜出<ref>{{cite news|title=Indonesia favorite to take on 2019 Asiad|url=http://www.shanghaidaily.com/sports/Indonesia-favorite-to-take-on-2019-Asiad/shdaily.shtml|accessdate=2014-04-19|newspaper=Shanghai Daily|date=2014-04-19|archive-date=2017-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171003230526/http://www.shanghaidaily.com/sports/Indonesia-favorite-to-take-on-2019-Asiad/shdaily.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，如果被选中，他们也愿意举办<ref>{{cite news|title=Indonesia 'proud' to host 2019 Asiad if selected|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/more-sports/others/Indonesia-proud-to-host-2019-Asiad-if-selected/articleshow/33953767.cms|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140419170847/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/more-sports/others/Indonesia-proud-to-host-2019-Asiad-if-selected/articleshow/33953767.cms|archivedate=2014-04-19|accessdate=2014-04-19|newspaper=The Times of India|date=2014-04-19|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。菲律宾<ref>{{cite news|last1=Alinea|first1=Eddie|title=POC bids to host next Asian Games|url=http://manilastandardtoday.com/2014/08/31/poc-bids-to-host-next-asian-games|accessdate=2014-09-05|publisher=Manila Standard Today|date=2014-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141105131847/http://manilastandardtoday.com/2014/08/31/poc-bids-to-host-next-asian-games|archive-date=2014-11-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>和印度也表示出兴趣，但印度迟迟未提交申办，亚奥理事会在延长期也没有接触到总理[[纳伦德拉·莫迪|纳伦德拉·莫迪]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=Ganguly|first1=Sudipto|title=India drops plans for late 2019 Asian Games bid|url=http://in.reuters.com/article/2014/07/07/asiangames-india-idINKBN0FC0HM20140707|accessdate=2014-07-07|publisher=Reuters India|date=2014-07-07|archive-date=2015-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150104090507/http://in.reuters.com/article/2014/07/07/asiangames-india-idINKBN0FC0HM20140707|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年5月5日，亚奥理事会考察雅加达、泗水、万隆和巨港等城市。当时泗水已主办[[2021年亚洲青年运动会|2021年亚洲青年运动会]]，放弃申办<ref>{{cite news|title=Kesiapan Indonesia Sebagai Calon Tuan Rumah AG 2019 Mulai Dievaluasi|url=http://www.pikiran-rakyat.com/node/280348|accessdate=2016-01-01|publisher=Pikiran Rakyat|date=2014-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160216170142/http://www.pikiran-rakyat.com/node/280348|archive-date=2016-02-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2014年7月25日，亚奥理事会在[[科威特城|科威特城]]选定雅加达为赛事举办城市，巨港协助举办。雅加达因设备齐全的运动设施、发达的交通网络以及宾馆和住宿等为宾客提供的设施，被亚奥理事会相中<ref>{{cite news|title=Setelah 1962, Jakarta Kembali Tuan Rumah Asian Games|author=Tjahjo Sasongko|date=2014-07-28|url=http://olahraga.kompas.com/read/2014/07/28/07035981/Setelah.1962.Jakarta.Kembali.Tuan.Rumah.Asian.Games|publisher=Kompas.com|language=id|accessdate=2014-07-29|archive-date=2014-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140729164501/http://olahraga.kompas.com/read/2014/07/28/07035981/Setelah.1962.Jakarta.Kembali.Tuan.Rumah.Asian.Games|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年9月20日，印尼签署主办合約<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ocasia.org/News/IndexNewsRM.aspx?WKegervtea38r+R3h5SSgw== |title=Indonesia to host 18th Asian Games in 2018 |accessdate=2016-01-01 |publisher=Olympic Council of Asia |date=2014-09-20 |archive-date=2014-09-21 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20140921100347/http://www.ocasia.org/News/IndexNewsRM.aspx?WKegervtea38r+R3h5SSgw== |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在2014年仁川亚运会闭幕式上，印尼象征性地被亚奥理事会任命为下届亚运会的举办地<ref>{{cite news|last1=Butler|first1=Nick|title=Asian Games: The Closing Ceremony|url=http://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1023024/asian-games-the-closing-ceremony|accessdate=2016-01-01|publisher=The Jakarta Post|date=2014-10-04|archive-date=2016-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160221051446/http://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1023024/asian-games-the-closing-ceremony|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Putri Utami|title=Menpora Janji Arena Asian Games 2018 Siap Tahun Ini|url=http://sports.okezone.com/read/2015/03/20/43/1121549/menpora-janji-arena-asian-games-2018-siap-tahun-ini|accessdate=2015-04-10|publisher=Okezone|language=id|date=2014-03-20|archive-date=2015-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150415160357/http://sports.okezone.com/read/2015/03/20/43/1121549/menpora-janji-arena-asian-games-2018-siap-tahun-ini|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=DP|first1=Yashinta|title=Pembukaan dan Penutupan Asian Games 2018 diadakan di Jakarta|url=http://www.antaranews.com/berita/518497/pembukaan-dan-penutupan-asian-games-2018-diadakan-di-jakarta|accessdate=2015-09-17|publisher=Antara News|date=2015-09-16|archive-date=2015-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016224021/http://www.antaranews.com/berita/518497/pembukaan-dan-penutupan-asian-games-2018-diadakan-di-jakarta|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

亚奥理事会原计划在2019年，而不是2018年举办赛事，这样赛事就能在[[2020年东京奥运会|2020年东京奥运会]]之前进行。印尼不希望赛事和2019年的[[2019年印度尼西亞總統選舉|總統選舉]]暨[[2019年印度尼西亞立法機構選舉|立法機構選舉]]冲突，亚奥理事会放弃了该计划<ref>{{cite news|last1=Davies|first1=Will|title=Indonesia to Host 2018 Asian Games|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/indonesia-to-host-2018-asian-games-1411189198|accessdate=2014-09-27|publisher=The Wall Street Journal|date=2014-09-20|archive-date=2015-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150627010551/http://www.wsj.com/articles/indonesia-to-host-2018-asian-games-1411189198|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1022643/asian-games-set-to-be-awarded-to-jakarta-but-in-2018-not-2019|title=Asian Games set to be awarded to Jakarta - but in 2018 not 2019|first=Nick|last=Butler|work=Inside the Games|access-date=2017-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170924045123/https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1022643/asian-games-set-to-be-awarded-to-jakarta-but-in-2018-not-2019|archive-date=2017-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 准备工作 ==
=== 花費 ===
赛事总开支约32亿美元<ref>{{cite news|url=https://financialtribune.com/articles/sports/85556/jakarta-asian-games-to-cost-32b-to-indonesia-economy|title=Jakarta Asian Games to Cost $3.2b to Indonesia Economy|newspaper=Financial Tribune|accessdate=2018-06-26|archive-date=2020-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200607023728/https://financialtribune.com/articles/sports/85556/jakarta-asian-games-to-cost-32b-to-indonesia-economy|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.tribunnews.com/sport/2017/03/25/wapres-nilai-anggaran-rp-30-triliun-untuk-asian-games-2018-telah-melalui-penghitungan-ulang|title=Wapres Nilai Anggaran Rp 30 Triliun untuk Asian Games 2018 Telah Melalui Penghitungan Ulang|newspaper=Tribun News|accessdate=2018-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180104073009/http://www.tribunnews.com/sport/2017/03/25/wapres-nilai-anggaran-rp-30-triliun-untuk-asian-games-2018-telah-melalui-penghitungan-ulang|archive-date=2018-01-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年，印尼中央政府拨出3万亿[[印尼盾|印尼盾]]的赛事筹备资金，其中部分资金由地方管理部门承担<ref name="facility">{{cite news|url=http://www.insidethegames.biz/major-games/asian-games/incheon-2015/1024762-preparations-for-jakarta-2018-asian-games-praised-by-oca-president|title=Preparations for Jakarta 2018 Asian Games praised by OCA President|last1=Goddard|first1=Emily|date=2015-01-08|accessdate=2015-01-11|publisher=inside the games|archive-date=2015-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150318142406/http://www.insidethegames.biz/major-games/asian-games/incheon-2015/1024762-preparations-for-jakarta-2018-asian-games-praised-by-oca-president|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不过，2018年6月公开的预算拨款为6.6万亿印尼盾，其中有8690亿来自赞助商<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://mediaindonesia.com/read/detail/170570-keterlibatan-sponsor-di-asian-games-perkecil-beban-pemerintah|title=Keterlibatan Sponsor di Asian Games Perkecil Beban Pemerintah|last=mediaindonesia.com|access-date=2018-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712091321/http://mediaindonesia.com/read/detail/170570-keterlibatan-sponsor-di-asian-games-perkecil-beban-pemerintah|archive-date=2018-07-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://sport.bisnis.com/read/20180711/59/815400/biaya-asian-games-2018-rawan-membengkak-inasgoc-cari-sponsor-baru|title=Biaya Asian Games 2018 Rawan Membengkak, Inasgoc Cari Sponsor Baru {{!}} sport - Bisnis.com|work=Bisnis.com|access-date=2018-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712090713/http://sport.bisnis.com/read/20180711/59/815400/biaya-asian-games-2018-rawan-membengkak-inasgoc-cari-sponsor-baru|archive-date=2018-07-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://nasional.kompas.com/read/2018/07/06/18560741/pemerintah-antisipasi-bengkaknya-anggaran-asian-games-karena-pelemahan|title=Pemerintah Antisipasi Bengkaknya Anggaran Asian Games karena Pelemahan Rupiah - Kompas.com|last=Media|first=Kompas Cyber|date=2018-07-06|work=KOMPAS.com|access-date=2018-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712095746/https://nasional.kompas.com/read/2018/07/06/18560741/pemerintah-antisipasi-bengkaknya-anggaran-asian-games-karena-pelemahan|archive-date=2018-07-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 推广 ===
{{Infobox character
| image = [[File:18th_Asian_Games_(Jakarta_Palembang_2018)_Official_Mascot-Lka,Atung,Bhin_Bhin.svg|250px]]
| name = Bhin Bhin宾宾（[[大极乐鸟|大极乐鸟]]）、Atung阿东（[[巴岛花鹿|巴岛花鹿]]）、Kaka卡卡（[[爪哇犀牛|爪哇犀牛]]）
| first = 2016年7月28日
| gender      = 未知
| creator = 大赛组委会
| species          =  Bhin Bhin（[[大极乐鸟|大极乐鸟]]）、Atung（[[巴岛花鹿|巴岛花鹿]]）、Kaka（[[爪哇犀牛|爪哇犀牛]]）
}}
会徽于2015年9月9日的印尼国家运动日公布，取材自印尼珍稀鸟类{{le|极乐鸟属|Cenderawasih|极乐鸟}}的形态<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2015/09/10/asian-games-logo-expected-inspire-high-performance.html|title=Asian Games logo expected to inspire high performance|last1=Prathivi|first1=Niken|date=2015-09-10|accessdate=2015-09-13|publisher=The Jakarta Post|archive-date=2020-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200910175858/https://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2015/09/10/asian-games-logo-expected-inspire-high-performance.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而许多人批评该设计过时，筹备方最终于2016年1月撤回这一设计方案。吉祥物Drawa也被斥和印尼文化和历史的关系不大，部分印尼人开玩笑说Drawa更像[[鸡|鸡]]，而不是极乐鸟。之后的设计方案公开招标最终收到了60份设计。2016年7月28日，最终方案“亚洲能量”（{{lang|en|''Energy of Asia''}}）正式出炉，设计取材于[[朋卡諾體育場主場館|朋卡諾體育場主場館]]，象征着亚洲各国的团结<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2016/01/07/ministry-change-logo-mascot-after-outcry.html|title=Ministry to change logo, mascot after outcry|last=Wardhani|first=Dewanti A.|website=The Jakarta Post|access-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160316075437/http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2016/01/07/ministry-change-logo-mascot-after-outcry.html|archive-date=2016-03-16|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1040089/official-logo-and-mascots-relaunched-for-2018-asian-games|title=Official logo and mascots relaunched for 2018 Asian Games|last=Etchells|first=Daniel|date=2016-07-29|work=Inside the Games|access-date=2017-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170711195709/http://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1040089/official-logo-and-mascots-relaunched-for-2018-asian-games|archive-date=2017-07-11|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="JP-AG-2018-Logo-Mascot">{{cite news|url=http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2016/07/29/ri-gets-down-to-business-with-new-logo-cute-mascots.html|title=RI gets down to business with new logo, cute mascots|author=Ina Parlina|date=2016-07-29|newspaper=The Jakarta Post|accessdate=2017-10-21|location=Jakarta|archive-date=2017-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170824222441/http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2016/07/29/ri-gets-down-to-business-with-new-logo-cute-mascots.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

三只新的吉祥物也在同日揭晓：Bhin Bhin是[[大极乐鸟|大极乐鸟]]、Atung是[[巴岛花鹿|巴岛花鹿]]、Kaka是[[爪哇犀牛|爪哇犀牛]]，分别象征着印尼东部、中部和西部地区以及谋略、速度和力量。每只吉祥物的服饰各不相同，Bhin Bhin穿着[[阿斯馬特族|阿斯馬特族]]图案的背心，Kaka穿着点缀着花卉图案的巨港传统服装，Atung穿着雅加达[[蜡染|蜡染]]图案的[[纱笼|纱笼]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161021194059/http://www.kemenpora.go.id/Asean-Games2016/LOGO-DAN%20MASKOT-ASIAN%20GAMES-2018.pdf|title=Logo & Mascot 18th Asian Games 2018|archivedate=2016-10-21|publisher=Kemenpora}}</ref>。

2017年8月18日，雅加达[[印尼国家纪念塔|印尼国家纪念塔]]和巨港{{le|库托贝撒堡|Kuto Besak}}公布举办赛事倒数一周年庆典。总统[[佐科·维多多|佐科·维多多]]出席雅加达的活动，期间[[韩流|韩流]]组合[[少女时代|少女时代]]的[[太妍|太妍]]和[[孝渊|孝渊]]登场表演。设立于{{le|欢迎纪念碑|Selamat Datang Monument}}和[[格羅拉·斯里維加亞體育場|格羅拉·斯里維加亞體育場]]前的倒计时钟揭晓<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://news.detik.com/foto-news/d-3599301/layar-hitung-mundur-asian-games-eksis-di-bundaran-hi|title=Layar Hitung Mundur Asian Games Eksis di Bundaran HI|last=Zafna|first=Grandyos|work=detiknews|access-date=2018-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206005906/https://news.detik.com/foto-news/d-3599301/layar-hitung-mundur-asian-games-eksis-di-bundaran-hi|archive-date=2017-12-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://jakartaglobe.id/eyewitness/asian-games-countdown/|title=Asian Games Countdown|work=Jakarta Globe|access-date=2018-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206074543/http://jakartaglobe.id/eyewitness/asian-games-countdown/|archive-date=2017-12-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年12月，亚洲多国举办欢乐跑活动，巴基斯坦的[[拉合尔|拉合尔]]是举办活动的首个城市<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ocasia.org/News/GetNewsbyNewsID?q=r/qFNh53kmEv71+Rj5JJd8wvicXb9FkK5hCf3UapHRs=|title=News - Olympic Council of Asia|website=www.ocasia.org|access-date=2018-07-12|archive-date=2020-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200607023823/https://ocasia.org/News/GetNewsbyNewsID?q=r%2FqFNh53kmEv71+Rj5JJd8wvicXb9FkK5hCf3UapHRs%3D|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2018年5月，赛事倒数100天活动举行，亚运圣火火炬登场。火炬灵感出自雅加达和巨港的传统武器golok和skin<ref>{{Cite news|first=Setyawatie|last=Wina|url=http://www.pikiran-rakyat.com/olah-raga/2018/05/10/beginilah-bentuk-obor-asian-games-2018-424164|title=Beginilah Bentuk Obor Asian Games 2018|work=Pikiran Rakyat|date=2018-05-10|accessdate=2018-08-03|language=id|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180731183854/http://www.pikiran-rakyat.com/olah-raga/2018/05/10/beginilah-bentuk-obor-asian-games-2018-424164|archive-date=2018-07-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2018年7月，印尼亚运会组织委员会对外公布金牌设计。设计采用亚运会标志和印尼各个地区的蜡染图案，反映印尼文化多样性及其团结。除此之外，蜡染团也反映赛事参赛国家的民族、宗教和种族多样性<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://en.antaranews.com/news/116426/asian-games-medals-reflect-indonesian-culture-inasgoc|title=Asian Games medals reflect Indonesian culture: Inasgoc - ANTARA News|last=antaranews.com|work=Antara News|access-date=2018-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712092911/https://en.antaranews.com/news/116426/asian-games-medals-reflect-indonesian-culture-inasgoc|archive-date=2018-07-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2018年7月13日，组委会发布赛事官方音乐专辑《{{le|2018年亚洲运动会：亚洲能量|Asian Games 2018: Energy of Asia}}》，其收录多名音乐人跨界操刀的13首歌曲<ref>{{cite news|url=https://entertainment.kompas.com/read/2018/07/13/163806410/semangati-para-atlet-lewat-album-asian-games-2018-energy-of-asia|title=Semangati Para Atlet lewat Album 'Asian Games 2018: Energy of Asia'|trans-title=Encourage athletes through the album 'Asian Games 2018: Energy of Asia'|newspaper=Kompas|language=id|first=Dian Reinis|last=Kumampung|date=2018-07-13|accessdate=2018-07-14|archive-date=2018-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180714112519/https://entertainment.kompas.com/read/2018/07/13/163806410/semangati-para-atlet-lewat-album-asian-games-2018-energy-of-asia|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 聖火接力 ===
2018年7月15日，圣火在[[1951年亚洲运动会|第1届亚洲运动会]]的举办地印度[[新德里|新德里]][[戴亞·昌德國家體育場|戴亞·昌德國家體育場]]采集<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=http://bola.republika.co.id/berita/sepakbola/arena-olahraga/18/01/30/p3ciqi428-api-asian-games-2018-berasal-dari-sinar-matahari|title=Api Asian Games 2018 Berasal dari Sinar Matahari {{!}} Republika Online|work=Republika Online|access-date=2018-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180205000842/http://bola.republika.co.id/berita/sepakbola/arena-olahraga/18/01/30/p3ciqi428-api-asian-games-2018-berasal-dari-sinar-matahari|archive-date=2018-02-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2018年7月18日，在[[日惹|日惹]]附近的[[普兰巴南|普兰巴南]]9世纪印度神庙梵天场举行的仪式上，从印度采集的圣火和[[中爪哇省|中爪哇省]]的[[长明灯|长明灯]]融合。随后，火炬接力音乐会举行，标志着全国范围的传递活动正式开始<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://regional.kompas.com/read/2018/07/18/22312941/di-candi-prambanan-2-legenda-atlet-indonesia-satukan-api-obor-asian-games|title=Di Candi Prambanan, 2 Legenda Atlet Indonesia Satukan Api Obor Asian Games 2018 - Kompas.com|last=Media|first=Kompas Cyber|date=2018-07-18|work=KOMPAS.com|access-date=2018-07-19|language=id|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180719085009/https://regional.kompas.com/read/2018/07/18/22312941/di-candi-prambanan-2-legenda-atlet-indonesia-satukan-api-obor-asian-games|archive-date=2018-07-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

圣火途径印尼18个省份的54座城市，最终在8月17日[[印度尼西亞獨立宣言|印尼独立日]]于国家纪念塔结束，之后会在翌日进入开幕式会场朋卡諾體育場主場館<ref name=":0" />。

== 場館建築 ==
[[雅加达|雅加达]]、[[南苏门答腊省|南苏门答腊省]]、[[万丹省|万丹省]]和[[西爪哇省|西爪哇省]]为赛事修建或翻新了场馆。赛事设施坐落于首都雅加达的三个运动区和巨港的一个运动区。然而，和雅加达接壤的西爪哇和万丹的15座比赛场地和11座训练场将用来支持比赛，因此比赛和训练用场总共80座。组委会利用现存场馆和设施，包括[[2011年东南亚运动会|2011年东南亚运动会]]场馆，希望节省开支。2018年2月的测试赛过后，组委会将部分比赛项目从[[雅加达国际博览会|雅加达国际博览会]]搬到[[雅加达会展中心|雅加达会展中心]]举行。

=== 雅加达 ===

雅加达[[朋卡諾體育場|朋卡諾體育場]]经过翻新，将独自举办13个项目。擁有55年歷史的[[朋卡諾體育場主場館|主体育场]]容量从88,000减少到76,127。为应对恐怖威胁，球场安装了[[面部识别|面部识别]]系统。位于[[东雅加达行政市|东雅加达行政市]]{{le|拉瓦芒溫|Rawamangun}}的[[雅加達國際自由車館|自行车场]]的建设耗资4000万美元，用于自行车、羽毛球、五人足球、篮球和摔跤比赛<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sport.tempo.co/read/774209/perusahaan-inggris-bangun-velodrome-asian-games-2018|title=Perusahaan Inggris Bangun Velodrome Asian Games 2018|newspaper=Tempo|accessdate=2018-01-03|archive-date=2020-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929172318/https://sport.tempo.co/read/774209/perusahaan-inggris-bangun-velodrome-asian-games-2018|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|普洛馬斯|Pulomas}}的[[雅加達國際馬術公園|马术公园]]的建造耗资3080万美元，佔地35公顷，配备100个马厩、运动员居所、兽医院、训练场地和停车场，能容纳1000名观众<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2017/10/14/pulo-mas-equestrian-facility-to-be-completed-next-month.html|title=Pulo Mas equestrian facility to be completed next month|newspaper=The Jakarta Post|accessdate=2018-01-03|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101020533/https://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2017/10/14/pulo-mas-equestrian-facility-to-be-completed-next-month.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

