=== 巨港 ===
[[File:Stadion-gelora-sriwijaya-palembang.jpg|thumb]]将举办女子足球决赛。]]
巨港的[[查卡峇靈體育城|查卡峇靈體育城]]承办其他项目赛事。园区新增并改善部分设施，其中[[格羅拉·斯里維加亞體育場|格羅拉·斯里維加亞體育場]]从3.6万座位升级到6万座位的扩展工程被取消，取而代之是将场内整个看台以及球场等设施改造，将座位减少到2.7万个<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://superball.bolasport.com/read/bola/liga-1/184773-direnovasi-kapasitas-stadion-jakabaring-berkurang|title=Direnovasi, Kapasitas Stadion Jakabaring Berkurang|work=superball.bolasport.com|access-date=2018-07-12|language=id|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712094201/https://superball.bolasport.com/read/bola/liga-1/184773-direnovasi-kapasitas-stadion-jakabaring-berkurang|archive-date=2018-07-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。查卡峇靈體育城新建的40道保龄球馆，于2018年5月底完工<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://olahraga.kompas.com/read/2018/05/31/04134958/app-sinar-mas-serahkan-jakabaring-bowling-center|title=APP Sinar Mas Serahkan Jakabaring Bowling Center - Kompas.com|last=Media|first=Kompas Cyber|date=2018-05-31|work=KOMPAS.com|access-date=2018-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712095406/https://olahraga.kompas.com/read/2018/05/31/04134958/app-sinar-mas-serahkan-jakabaring-bowling-center|archive-date=2018-07-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外还新增了八个网球场<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.viva.co.id/foto/sport/19253-penambahan-lapangan-tenis-untuk-asian-games-2017|title=Penambahan Lapangan Tenis untuk ASIAN Games 2017 – VIVA|last=VIVA|first=PT. VIVA MEDIA BARU -|website=www.viva.co.id|language=id|access-date=2018-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712085100/https://www.viva.co.id/foto/sport/19253-penambahan-lapangan-tenis-untuk-asian-games-2017|archive-date=2018-07-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。查卡峇靈湖的轻艇和皮划艇场地长度扩展到2300米，还由新建的赛艇设施和岸边的看台<ref>{{cite news|url=http://sp.beritasatu.com/home/sumsel-siap-gelar-18-cabang-olahraga-asian-games-2018/79845|title=Sumsel Siap Gelar 18 Cabang Olahraga Asian Games 2018|date=2015-03-03|accessdate=2015-04-10|publisher=Suara Pembaruan|language=id|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181004235327/http://sp.beritasatu.com/home/sumsel-siap-gelar-18-cabang-olahraga-asian-games-2018/79845|archive-date=2018-10-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。现有的场馆也经过翻修，其中拉瑙體育館成为藤球场馆<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.klikampera.com/jelang-asian-games-istaf-apresiasi-persiapan-gor-ranau/|title=Jelang Asian Games, ISTAF Apresiasi Persiapan GOR Ranau - klikampera|date=2018-03-28|work=klikampera|access-date=2018-07-19|language=id|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180719173803/https://www.klikampera.com/jelang-asian-games-istaf-apresiasi-persiapan-gor-ranau/|archive-date=2018-07-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

