=== -{zh-tw:選手村;zh-cn:运动员村}- ===
[[File:AG18_Athlete_Village_Kemayoran.jpg|240px]]
本屆亞運會的-{zh-tw:選手村;zh-cn:运动员村}-位于{{le|玛腰兰|Kemayoran}}，共有10座塔楼7424套公寓，占地10[[公顷|公顷]]。总容纳人数为22272人，超越国际奥委会需要主办城市为1.4万名运动会提供客房的标准。巨港[[查加巴灵体育城|查加巴灵体育城]]的-{zh-tw:選手村;zh-cn:运动员村}-容纳3000名运动员和官员<ref>{{cite news|url=http://megapolitan.kompas.com/read/2015/01/07/18063451/Jelang.Asian.Games.2018.DKI.Akan.Bangun.Kampung.Atlet.di.Kemayoran|title=Jelang Asian Games 2018, DKI Akan Bangun Kampung Atlet di Kemayoran|last1=Aziza|first1=Kurnia Sari|date=2015-01-07|accessdate=2015-01-07|publisher=KOMPAS|last2=Afrianti|first2=Desy|archive-date=2020-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200408113521/http://megapolitan.kompas.com/read/2015/01/07/18063451/Jelang.Asian.Games.2018.DKI.Akan.Bangun.Kampung.Atlet.di.Kemayoran|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2016/03/19/govt-build-10-apartment-towers-athletes-kemayoran.html|title=Govt to build 10 apartment towers for athletes in Kemayoran|newspaper=The Jakarta Post|accessdate=2018-01-03|archive-date=2020-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200408113523/http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2016/03/19/govt-build-10-apartment-towers-athletes-kemayoran.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 交通 ===
[[File:LRT_Palembang_Ampera_Station.jpg|thumb]]
[[雅加达地铁|雅加达地铁]]和[[雅加达轻轨|雅加达轻轨]]施工进度加快，争取在比赛前完工<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.beritasatu.com/megapolitan/238690-hadapi-asian-games-2018-djarot-minta-pembangunan-mrt-dikebut.html|title=Hadapi Asian Games 2018, Djarot Minta Pembangunan MRT Dikebut|last1=Tristia Tambun|first1=Lenny|date=2015-01-07|accessdate=2015-01-11|publisher=Berita Satu|language=id|archive-date=2020-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200607023937/https://www.beritasatu.com/megapolitan/238690-hadapi-asian-games-2018-djarot-minta-pembangunan-mrt-dikebut.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其中一条轻轨线路连接[[中雅加达行政市|中雅加达行政市]]{{le|玛腰兰|Kemayoran}}运动员村和[[东雅加达行政市|东雅加达行政市]]{{le|普洛加东|Rawamangun}}[[自行车场|自行车场]]。市内巴士运营商[[雅加达专线巴士|雅加达专线巴士]]新增416条线路服务官员<ref>{{cite news|last1=Ibnu Aqil|first1=Andi Muhammad|title=Transjakarta gets 416 new buses ahead of Asian Games|url=http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2018/07/13/transjakarta-gets-416-new-buses-ahead-of-asian-games.html|accessdate=2018-07-13|work=The Jakarta Post|publisher=thejakartapost.com|date=2018-07-13|archive-date=2020-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200910183446/https://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2018/07/13/transjakarta-gets-416-new-buses-ahead-of-asian-games.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并在比赛期间特定日期提供免费乘车服务<ref>{{cite news|url=http://jakartaglobe.id/sports/indonesia-aims-to-better-incheons-asian-games-record-in-spectator-numbers/|title=Indonesia Aims to Better Incheon's Asian Games Record in Spectator Numbers|newspaper=Jakarta Globe|date=2018-08-10|accessdate=2018-08-10|archive-date=2018-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180810180207/http://jakartaglobe.id/sports/indonesia-aims-to-better-incheons-asian-games-record-in-spectator-numbers/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

巨港也对当地的公共交通设施进行升格，其中包括修建了[[苏丹马哈茂德巴达鲁丁二世机场|苏丹马哈茂德巴达鲁丁二世机场]]（巨港机场）至查加巴灵运动城的25公里[[巨港轻轨|轻轨线路]]，并于2018年6月投入使用<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.antaranews.com/en/news/100175/south-sumatra-to-build-monorail-for-2018-asian-games|title=South Sumatra to build monorail for 2018 Asian Games|date=2015-08-26|accessdate=2015-08-29|publisher=Antara News|archive-date=2016-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160822012351/http://www.antaranews.com/en/news/100175/south-sumatra-to-build-monorail-for-2018-asian-games|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://palembang.tribunnews.com/2018/07/19/beroperasi-tangal-23-juli-2018-warga-palembang-tak-sabar-naik-lrt-harga-tiket-flat-rp-5000|title=Beroperasi Tangal 23 Juli 2018. Warga Palembang tak Sabar Naik LRT. Harga Tiket Flat Rp 5.000 - Sriwijaya Post|date=2018-07-19|work=Sriwijaya Post|access-date=2018-07-19|language=id|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180719084019/http://palembang.tribunnews.com/2018/07/19/beroperasi-tangal-23-juli-2018-warga-palembang-tak-sabar-naik-lrt-harga-tiket-flat-rp-5000|archive-date=2018-07-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>，巨港机场也扩建了进出港航站楼以提升载客量，并修建行人天桥和轻轨站台连接<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thejakartapost.com/travel/2016/10/14/palembang-airport-to-be-revamped-for-2018-asian-games.html|title=Palembang airport to be revamped for 2018 Asian Games|date=2016-10-14|work=Jakarta Post|accessdate=2016-10-20|publisher=thejakartapost.com|archive-date=2017-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170823170025/http://www.thejakartapost.com/travel/2016/10/14/palembang-airport-to-be-revamped-for-2018-asian-games.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。城内还修建了收费公路、高架桥和大桥<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rmolsumsel.com/read/2015/03/09/24750/Jadi-Tuan-Rumah,-Pemkot-Targetkan-2017-Siap-Sambut-Asian-Games-|title=Jadi Tuan Rumah, Pemkot Targetkan 2017 Siap Sambut Asian Games|date=2015-03-09|accessdate=2017-10-21|publisher=Rakyat Merdeka Online Sumsel|language=id|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180706104031/http://www.rmolsumsel.com/read/2015/03/09/24750/Jadi-Tuan-Rumah,-Pemkot-Targetkan-2017-Siap-Sambut-Asian-Games-|archive-date=2018-07-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

