== 赛事 ==
[[File:2018_Asian_Games_opening_ceremony_14_(cropped).jpg|thumb]]
=== 开闭幕式 ===
{{main|2018年亞洲運動會開幕禮|2018年亞洲運動會閉幕禮}}
闭幕式原定由巨港举办<ref>{{cite news|last1=Al-Yamani|first1=Zaky|last2=Ilham Rafles|first2=Riki|title=Pembukaan Asian Games 2018 Batal di Palembang|url=http://sport.viva.co.id/news/read/675160-pembukaan-asian-games-2018-batal-di-palembang|accessdate=2015-09-17|publisher=VIVA|date=2015-09-17|archive-date=2016-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160915020842/http://sport.viva.co.id/news/read/675160-pembukaan-asian-games-2018-batal-di-palembang|dead-url=no}}</ref>，后来雅加达主办开闭幕式<ref>{{cite news|title=Minister: 2018 Asian Games Closing Ceremony in Palembang|url=http://jakartaglobe.beritasatu.com/sports/minister-2018-asian-games-closing-ceremony-palembang/|first=Hendro|last=Situmorang|date=2015-09-05|accessdate=2015-09-13|publisher=Jakarta Globe|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907201953/http://jakartaglobe.beritasatu.com/sports/minister-2018-asian-games-closing-ceremony-palembang|archive-date=2015-09-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

闭幕式于2018年9月2日晚举行，除了当地艺术家表演和杭州时间外，印度歌手、韩国男子团体[[Super_Junior|Super Junior]]和[[iKON|iKON]]也登台表演<ref>{{cite web|url=https://en.asiangames2018.id/about/closing-ceremony|title=Closing Ceremony Asian Games 2018|website=asiangames2018.id|access-date=2018-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180830110241/https://en.asiangames2018.id/about/closing-ceremony|archive-date=2018-08-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

=== 參賽國家和地區 ===
和[[2018年冬季奥林匹克运动会朝韩联队|2018年冬季奥运会]]相同，南北韓在開幕典禮時持[[統一旗|統一旗]]進場<ref>{{cite news|last1=Riotta|first1=Chris|title=North and South Korea agree to joint teams for Asian Games|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/north-korea-nuclear-peace-talks-south-korea-asian-games-team-basketball-pyongyang-a8405446.html|accessdate=2018-08-14|work=Independent|publisher=independent.co.uk|date=2018-06-19|archive-date=2018-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180814171455/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/north-korea-nuclear-peace-talks-south-korea-asian-games-team-basketball-pyongyang-a8405446.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
