=== 比賽項目 ===
2017年3月，亚奥理事会宣布本届比赛项目共设42个大项484个小项，包括[[2016年里约奥运会|2016年-{里}-約奧運會]]的28个永久奥运项目、[[2020年东京奥运会|2020年东京奥运会]]新增的5个项目及其他非奥运项目<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1047759/forty-two-sports-confirmed-for-2018-asian-games|title=Forty-two sports confirmed for 2018 Asian Games|first=Max|last=Winters|work=InsideTheGames|date=2017-03-06|access-date=2017-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170624001120/http://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1047759/forty-two-sports-confirmed-for-2018-asian-games|archive-date=2017-06-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年4月，亚奥理事会考虑到削减开支，取消[[摔跤|摔跤]]、[[板球|板球]]、[[古拉什|古拉什]]、[[滑板运动|滑板运动]]、[[桑搏|桑搏]]和[[冲浪|冲浪]]比赛，[[桥牌|桥牌]]、[[水上摩托车|水上摩托车]]、[[柔术|柔术]]、[[滑翔伞|滑翔伞]]、[[運動攀登|運動攀登]]、[[跆拳道|跆拳道]]（尤其是非奥运重量级）和[[武术|武术]]比赛数量减少，调整后的项目总数为431个<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1049411/exclusive-cricket-and-sambo-among-sports-removed-from-2018-asian-games-programme|title=Exclusive: Cricket and sambo among sports removed from 2018 Asian Games programme|last=Butler|first=Nick|date=2017-04-19|website=Inside the Games|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170801175423/http://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1049411/exclusive-cricket-and-sambo-among-sports-removed-from-2018-asian-games-programme|archive-date=2017-08-01|dead-url=no|access-date=2017-07-21}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://indianexpress.com/article/sports/cricket/cricket-removed-from-2018-asian-games-programme-4621045/|title=Cricket removed from 2018 Asian Games programme|date=2017-04-20|work=The Indian Express|access-date=2017-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170726214328/http://indianexpress.com/article/sports/cricket/cricket-removed-from-2018-asian-games-programme-4621045/|archive-date=2017-07-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

项目的最终安排于2017年9月公布，总数增至40个大项462个小项，属亚运史上第二多。新增2020年东京奥运会项目[[3x3_(篮球)|3x3篮球]]和{{le|自由式小轮车|Freestyle BMX}}<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1055574/forty-sports-and-462-events-included-in-final-programme-for-jakarta-2018|title=Forty sports and 462 events included in final programme for Jakarta 2018|work=Inside the Games|access-date=2018-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180331040711/https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1055574/forty-sports-and-462-events-included-in-final-programme-for-jakarta-2018|archive-date=2018-03-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

此外，亚运史上第一次将[[电子竞技|电子竞技]]和[[轻艇水球|轻艇水球]]列为表演项目，其中电子竞技设置六款比赛游戏<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.indosport.com/multisport/20170418/esports-akan-dipertandingkan-di-asian-games|title=Esports Akan Dipertandingkan di Asian Games|first=Arum Kusuma|last=Dewi|date=2017-04-18|work=INDOSPORT.com|access-date=2017-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170820163233/http://www.indosport.com/multisport/20170418/esports-akan-dipertandingkan-di-asian-games|archive-date=2017-08-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

